                        Blackfeet Community Hospital

                              MISSION STATEMENT

     The Blackfeet Community Hospital is to improve the health and well
        being of the community by providing compassionate, caring and
   accessible health care. Our vision is to achieve and sustain excellence
       in quality of care and personal service through a commitment to
                           patients and employees.


